lead_paragraph: Fifth seed Simona Halep narrowly avoided a third-round upset with a 6-1 2-6 6-4 win over Hungary's Timea Babos on Saturday to keep her U.S. Open title hopes alive.

headline.print_headline: Halep Gets Hungarian Fright Before Reaching Last 16
